name: Goodbydao
body:
GoodbyDao
=========

A fully functional generic DAO library.


features:

  - Simple and comprehensive API.
  - CDI support.
  - easy extensible.
  - Hibernate, EclipseLink, BatooJPA, OpenJPA, JDBC Tested!
  - a Sample Spring-Hibernate-GoodbyDao test project have been provided.
